title: Kraftwerk rape.avi
description:
Just a weird rape scene from an old Brazilian movie. The weird thing is the music, hence the name of the file Kraftwerk rape. I guess the german techno-godfathers didn't imagine this as an appropriate use for their music as a soundtrack.

The quality of the vhs-tape stinks, sorry.

The scene is from the movie "A menina do sexo diabolico" from 1987 also known as "Vinganca diabolica". The girls name is Makerley Reis.
